        void observerNotify(java.lang.String eventType,
                  T state)
        Called by the observable for all observers, to notify upon some event
        Parameters:
        eventType - Used to categorize the type of event, e.g. item added, item removed, etc.
        state - Some state passed by the observable to the observer e.g. the subject item that was added/removed/etc.
